{"tid":2179322,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【六四冇死人】【721係勢均力敵，旗鼓相當】【王毅係全地球最能幹既外長】「現在中國全國每天都是零感染啊！」","createTime":"2020-08-29T04:28:44.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-29T06:11:48.000Z","uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3cd44b6e75e60f4e700e5846ec504d02762c0b75","tid":2179322,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T04:28:44.000Z","msg":"正在挪威訪問的中國外長王毅表示，中國是首先向世衛通報疫情的國家，但並不意味味道疫情就發源於中國。他指出病毒起源是一個科學問題，不能把它政治化，標籤化。他 又說：「現在中國全國每天都是零感染啊！所以所謂的病毒從中國傳出去，都是謊言！」<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://twitter.com/rfa_chinese/status/1299273427535015937?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frfa_chinese%2Fstatus%2F1299273427535015937%3Fs%3D21&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5ZqEbpHCTTcQcXY6VsQHNTK4%3D&h=a4d49c59\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Frfa_chinese%2Fstatus%2F1299273427535015937%3Fs%3D21&h=dff36b65\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/rfa_chinese/status/1299273427535015937?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"3efb605d347f51446ee0194b6c07b1623a6cf285","tid":2179322,"uid":242537,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T04:29:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2caPHST.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2caPHST.jpg&h=70a8b8c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e14139199d50d91f8f73abbe19e4afd9fa0753f3","tid":2179322,"uid":13955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T04:30:11.000Z","msg":"香港獨立左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b101dff4e557aacc269e3d24208f2e2c9b45a141","tid":2179322,"uid":71071,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T04:30:31.000Z","msg":"遲D應該死咗嗰D會番生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />最後零dead case"},{"pid":"b931ae44c0bd6105acae0591159e8fb6a637e931","tid":2179322,"uid":242537,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e14139199d50d91f8f73abbe19e4afd9fa0753